              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "D4PI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Distributed in polyethylene moderator along",
                "      three concentric circles with diameters of 106,",
                "      160 and 220 mm assemblage of 30 boron counters",
                "      SNM-11 was used for neutron detection. Energy",
                "      Dependence of detector absolute efficiency was",
                "      determined by two different methods:",
                "    1 Activation method based on the 51-V(P,N) reaction",
                "    2 Method based on the measurements of the average",
                "      number of prompt neutrons from 252-Cf source",
                "      spontaneous fission.",
                "      The relative efficiency of neutron detector",
                "      was determined by Monte-Carlo calculations"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  Semiconductor surface-barrier detector for",
